ss=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 30, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lkv1665703134628.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lkv1665703134628.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lkv1665703134628.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lkv1665703134628\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__uinst_uf_404800\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy an instance handle to a parameter or entity field of type <code class=\"ph codeph\">handle</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__topic_d121322e1_d121323e1_d121324e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lkv1665703134628_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__codeblock_dhy_4bb_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uinst2uf (UHACThOpr, intseqNr, UHACThInst);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__topic_d86112e1_d86113e1_d86114e1_d86115e1_d86116e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959014e64\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__parml_gc5_pbb_1wb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hOpr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle to the operation or entity parameter.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the basic parameter or entity field (sequence numbers start\n                  with 1).</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hInst</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Instance handle.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__topic_d86117e1_d86118e1_d86119e1_d86120e1_d86121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959014e103\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__d6412e20\">See the \"Call-In API Return Codes\" topic. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__topic_d86122e1_d86123e1_d86124e1_d86125e1_d86126e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959014e112\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__topic_d86127e1_d86128e1_d86129e1_d86130e1_d86131e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959014e124\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__p_d121355e1_d121356e1_d121357e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uinst2uf</code> copies an instance handle\n            from your program to a basic parameter or entity field of type <code class=\"ph codeph\">handle</code>.\n            This function can be used to pass instance handles from 3GL to 4GL.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__section_q33_dcb_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959014e138\">Example: uinst2uf</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example describes how to pass a 3GL-generated instance\n            handle to 4GL so it can be used in ProcScript. First we create an instance of the\n            service SERV2. Then we activate the operation PUTHANDLE in service TESTSVC, passing it\n            the instance handle of SERV2 as an IN parameter. The service PUTHANDLE will then\n            activate the operation HELLO in service SERV2, using the instance handle.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation PUTHANDLE in service TESTSVC is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lkv1665703134628_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__codeblock_nh2_fcb_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation puthandle\nparams\nhandle hInst : in\nendparams\n\nactivate hInst-&gt;Hello()\nif ( $status &lt; 0 )\nputmess \"puthandle: status = %%$status\"\nputmess \"%%$procerrorcontext\"\nendif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation HELLO in service SERV2 is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lkv1665703134628_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__codeblock_zsx_gcb_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation hello\nputmess \"Hello from SERV2.hello() !!!\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">This is the 3GL code:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104lkv1665703134628_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"lkv1665703134628__codeblock_ytj_3cb_1wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\ntest_handle2 ()\n{\nUHACT hEnv; /* Environment handle */\nUHACT hIn1, hIn2; /* Instance handles */\nUHACT hOp1; /* Operation handle */\nlong actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */\n\n/* Get environment handle */\nueopen(&amp;hEnv);\n/* Instantiate service SERV2 */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"SERV2\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn2, &amp;procErr);\n\n/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn1, &amp;procErr);\n\n/* Instantiate operation RUNSERV2 */\nuinstopr(hIn1,(UCHAR *)\"PUTHANDLE\", 0, &amp;hOp1);\nuinst2uf(hOp1, 1, hIn2);\n\nuopract (hOp1, &amp;actStatus, &amp;procErr); /* Activate operation RUNSERV2 */\n\nuinstdel (hIn1, 0); /* Destroy instance */\nufreeh (&amp;hOp1); /* Free RUNSERV2 operation handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn1); /* Free instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn2); /* Free instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hEnv); /* Free environment handle */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jhh1665702691902.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Call-In API Return Codes</a><p>Codes that can possibly be returned by functions from the 3GL call-in API are consistent with the values returned by the ProcScript function $procerror, unless noted otherwise.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wgr1665703134698.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uuf2inst</a><p>Copy a basic parameter or entity field of type handle to a program variable.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529613\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529613\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uinst2uf Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 30, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy an instance handle to a parameter or entity field of type handle . Explain this code long uinst2uf (UHACThOpr, intseqNr, UHACThInst); Copy Parameters hOpr Handle to the operation or entity parameter. seqNr Sequence number of the basic parameter or entity field (sequence numbers start with 1). hInst Instance handle. Return Values See the \"Call-In API Return Codes\" topic. Use Library: ucall Description uinst2uf copies an instance handle from your program to a basic parameter or entity field of type handle . This function can be used to pass instance handles from 3GL to 4GL. Example: uinst2uf The following example describes how to pass a 3GL-generated instance handle to 4GL so it can be used in ProcScript. First we create an instance of the service SERV2. Then we activate the operation PUTHANDLE in service TESTSVC, passing it the instance handle of SERV2 as an IN parameter. The service PUTHANDLE will then activate the operation HELLO in service SERV2, using the instance handle. The operation PUTHANDLE in service TESTSVC is defined as follows: Explain this code operation puthandle params handle hInst : in endparams activate hInst->Hello() if ( $status < 0 ) putmess \"puthandle: status = %%$status\" putmess \"%%$procerrorcontext\" endif end Copy The operation HELLO in service SERV2 is defined as follows: Explain this code operation hello putmess \"Hello from SERV2.hello() !!!\" end Copy This is the 3GL code: Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> test_handle2 () { UHACT hEnv; /* Environment handle */ UHACT hIn1, hIn2; /* Instance handles */ UHACT hOp1; /* Operation handle */ long actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */ /* Get environment handle */ ueopen(&hEnv); /* Instantiate service SERV2 */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"SERV2\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn2, &procErr); /* Instantiate service TESTSVC */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn1, &procErr); /* Instantiate operation RUNSERV2 */ uinstopr(hIn1,(UCHAR *)\"PUTHANDLE\", 0, &hOp1); uinst2uf(hOp1, 1, hIn2); uopract (hOp1, &actStatus, &procErr); /* Activate operation RUNSERV2 */ uinstdel (hIn1, 0); /* Destroy instance */ ufreeh (&hOp1); /* Free RUNSERV2 operation handle */ ufreeh (&hIn1); /* Free instance handle */ ufreeh (&hIn2); /* Free instance handle */ ufreeh (&hEnv); /* Free environment handle */ } Copy Related Links Call-In API Return Codes Codes that can possibly be returned by functions from the 3GL call-in API are consistent with the values returned by the ProcScript function $procerror, unless noted otherwise. uuf2inst Copy a basic parameter or entity field of type handle to a program variable. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}